Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:04.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:10.09,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:17.23,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:24.48,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.56,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:34.05,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:41.84,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.70,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.65,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:54.01,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:57.64,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.41,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:05.20,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.75,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:14.13,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:18.88,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.06,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.73,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:27.94,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:17.23,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}用现在覆盖过去  未来就是这样步步走近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:24.48,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如此理所当然  却依旧心殇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.56,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那天你我所见的『世界』  再一次拼凑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:34.05,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}愿望实现之时若能到来  我再无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:41.84,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使被人嘲笑不切实际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.70,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}直到再见你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:54.01,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}纵使颠沛轮回的命运再艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:57.64,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我也绝对  绝对  不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.41,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『明天再见』  那一份『未来』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:05.20,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}让我们一直珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.75,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}一旦开始  再无休止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:14.13,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}现在我只愿和你一起  去瞭望梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:18.88,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}紧握的双手  不会再分离
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:17.08,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心では何度も　好きと伝えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:27.55,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想いは残るの？　わたし消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:37.56,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君の声　真っ直ぐな瞳　忘れない温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:46.29,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}記憶の中に閉じ込めたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:52.60,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}変えられないこと　変えてしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:23:02.85,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何度でも運命の中を　笑いあって　ふざけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:08.63,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「明日また会えるよね」　きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:19.71,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会いたい　ただひとつだけ願い叶うなら
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:17.08,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在心中曾千百次  向你表述过爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:27.55,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否会留下情思  即便我终会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:37.56,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你的声响  直视的目光  是无法忘怀的暖阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:46.29,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要烙刻在记忆上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:52.60,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}无从改变之物  却又想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:23:02.85,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断在轮回命运中  一同嬉笑  一同玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:08.63,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一定能够「明天再会」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:19.71,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愿与你相会  若这唯一的祈愿将能实现
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  要是结成功阻止了佳织的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时  结会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和现在一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了避免造成更大的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会进入休眠模式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…  其实你已经意识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在佳织没有遭遇事故的未来里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就没有必要再制造结了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那岂不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结的未来真的还能继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让结进入休眠模式  这样就能完事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实结她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  结呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳织  是不是发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说自己马上就会消失不见…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想起了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搞不清楚  但是为什么她会露出那样的神情来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢谁是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结  你对奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:01:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:35.05,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,302)}『明天我们  还会再见吧？』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为昨天的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏的那副表情我是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊  理科的野田老师经常弄错上课的时间  真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要到文化节了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  没事的话古川也来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我也很想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加油的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  我的堂弟也会来看文化节的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还只是个初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常讨人喜欢呢  总觉得他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天  对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说了  我没什么想和你谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在食堂吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒懒散散的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  不是说要去看星星的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦确实  抱歉  延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没那个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她  现在会不会在天台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？  不好意思  你说什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明就是根本没有容身之处的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙学姐  你在这儿干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚吃了午饭  有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找结的话  她可不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难得呢  奏会为某个人如此上心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  可能是我想得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得结经常会看着我  一副欲言又止的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这个非常在意  没法放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全裸晕倒在五楼这点也很让人费解  身上尽是些迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她跟其他的女孩给人的感觉也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计她是想起了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟经常看到她在想什么心事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏是被尽是谜团的她吸引住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚你究竟打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可不能逃避或是敷衍某人的感情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是那么做了的话  我可不原谅你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚刚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  那之后古川同学都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是「中纳言参上」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先这里「参」是谦让语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等于…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  10月14日  16时20分  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要将佐佐木佳织从在这儿发生的公交事故中拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  要让现在的结理解这些果然还是有点困难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能救出佐佐木佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏和爱理  会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  当然会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有些必须传达给佳织的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳织无论在哪个时间轴上  都向奏告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但奏却一次也没能明确地回应过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才制造了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果造就这因果的锁链的不是那场事故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是和奏对佳织的感情有关的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  请问见到过一个穿着校服留着长发的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样  要是能救下佳织的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你道歉  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再追问什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能一直待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次来这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦  你才来没多久嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直生活在内滨的我倒是早就见惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养育了奏的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所不知道的奏的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到镇上走走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是内滨商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他地方的超市相比  这里的东西物廉价美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和佳织的共识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山同学在家里也是会做饭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是轮流来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想吃一次试试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里  是我和佳织上过的幼儿园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过以前比现在这个破旧不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼儿园里的秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想象不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候可可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾是幼儿园的偶像哦  佳织她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候就和佳织认识了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她小时候比现在更爱哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏跟佳织原来是一起长大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}但是她并不怕生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}说起来  在我的小学郊游的时候她也跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我们那时候也不知道什么  换车的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我居然希望我跟奏的两个人的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能一直就这样持续下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领队的老师发现了  结果闹得可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  我  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再陪我一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也告诉凪沙学姐一声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是在内滨看星星最漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天本来是应该和大家一起来这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和原先预计的不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过反正大家对星星也不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋季四边形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室宿二  壁宿二  壁宿一  室宿一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直往下  最亮的那颗就是北落师门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢星星的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样无数次一起仰望星空的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.5}希望今天明天还有从此以后也能像这样悠悠闲闲懒懒洋洋地过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏所期望的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将奏的笑容延续到未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星要是哪天真能实现许下的愿望就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许真有这么一天也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是秋山同学的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  如果愿望实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结也许了什么愿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜托秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天放学后  请一定要把佳织带到活动室来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事  明天佳织应该会向你表白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时  你一定要回应她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊  为什么突然说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天佳织的便当看起来真的好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你和结发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏啊  男人总是要有下决定的时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳织  我有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在想  必须和你谈一次才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我前天突然从家里跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我才是呢  是不是多嘴了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对秋山同学并没有什么特殊感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我和结才认识不久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总觉得我和你在什么地方有些相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我冥冥之中能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的不是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想向奏表明自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会因为这个受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还会伤害到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一直这样下去永远也不会有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结你觉得这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川同学  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再见喽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那么我希望各位今后也能度过健康的校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是像家人或兄妹那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是另一种的  喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎么了  结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微转转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么我也是会长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱理？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说  结她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在找结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚才出去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才总感觉她样子有些怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你去安慰一下佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果奏心中没能回应表白的心结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了一个因果的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只要奏回应了佳织的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不会是事故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  奏  奏！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是奏你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我太担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要让我追多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事还要通知警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  佳织呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回应了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉佳织  我喜欢结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近总是在想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你不要再露出寂寞的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望你能陪在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想更加地了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法对自己撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我终于
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也  喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心被卷进事故了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  奏你总是傻傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我担心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳织你也要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟比我还笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你是一个人来这里的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？这样人就全了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…
